ğŸš€ How to Start Writing This Project
Start with the Entity (Student.java) â†’ defines your DB structure.

Configure Hibernate (hibernate.cfg.xml) â†’ connects Java to MySQL.

Write DAO (StudentDAO.java) â†’ handles DB operations.

Create Servlets (RegisterServlet, ViewStudentsServlet) â†’ handle requests.

Design JSP/HTML pages (register.html, success.jsp, viewStudents.jsp) â†’ user interface.

Map everything in web.xml â†’ connects URLs to Servlets.

